                    revenue recognition implementation issues for brokers and dealers in securities
                    applying FASB ASC 606 and related interpretations from the FASB/IASB Joint
                    Transition Resource Group for Revenue Recognition (TRG). <unknown id="UUID-7fd03ea1-9f8d-9559-2b2e-9d777be1f8cd_N661755d19f6a4" class="- topic/unknown ">Chapter 5</unknown>
